    seoDescription: { en: 'Calculate the exact number of days between any two dates, track countdowns to important events, and never miss another anniversary or birthday. Our free online date calculator helps you plan for upcoming holidays, track relationship milestones, calculate project deadlines, and determine age differences with precision. Perfect for personal life planning, event preparation, and project management.', zh: '精确计算任意两个日期之间的天数，追踪重要事件的倒计时，再也不错过任何纪念日或生日。免费在线日期计算器帮助您规划即将到来的节假日、追踪关系里程碑、计算项目截止日期和确定年龄差异。适用于个人生活规划、活动准备和项目管理的完美工具。' },
    seoContent: { en: 'Keeping track of important dates can be surprisingly challenging in our busy lives. Whether it is counting how many days you have been together with your partner, planning how many days remain until a wedding or birthday, calculating project deadlines, or simply wondering exactly how many days passed between two historical events — our Date Calculator handles it all with precision and elegance. Enter any start and end date, and instantly get the exact number of days, weeks, months, and years between them. The built-in countdown feature shows you precisely how long until your next special occasion in days, hours, and minutes, creating a beautiful visual reminder that builds excitement. Popular use cases include tracking relationship anniversaries ("how many days have we been together?"), pregnancy countdowns, exam preparation countdowns, project milestone tracking, age difference calculations, and planning for holidays like Christmas, New Year, Chinese Spring Festival, Valentine is Day, and more. The tool accounts for leap years and varying month lengths automatically, so you always get mathematically precise results. Ideal for couples wanting to celebrate milestones, students preparing for important exams, project managers tracking sprint deadlines, event planners coordinating multiple timelines, and anyone who values remembering what truly matters in life.', zh: '在忙碌的生活中，记住重要日期可能出人意料地困难。无论是计算和恋人在一起了多少天、计划距离婚礼或生日还有多久、计算项目截止日期，还是单纯想知道两个历史事件之间恰好隔了多少天——我们的纪念日倒计时计算器都能精确而优雅地处理一切。输入任意开始和结束日期，即刻获得它们之间的精确天数、周数、月数和年数。内置倒计时功能精确显示距离下一个特殊时刻还有多少天、多少小时和多少分钟，创造美丽的视觉提醒，让期待感不断累积。常见使用场景包括追踪恋爱纪念日（"我们在一起多少天了？"）、孕期倒计时、考试备考倒计时、项目里程碑追踪、年龄差计算，以及圣诞节、新年、春节、情人节等节假日的倒计时规划。工具自动考虑闰年和每月天数差异，确保结果始终数学精确。非常适合想要庆祝里程碑的情侣、准备重要考试的学生、追踪冲刺截止日期的项目经理、协调多条时间线的活动策划者，以及任何珍视生命中重要时刻的人。' }
