    seoTitle: { en: 'Online QR Code Scanner - Decode QR from Images Without Phone', zh: '在线二维码识别器 - 无需手机即可从图片解码二维码' },
    seoDescription: { en: 'Decode QR codes directly from image files on your computer without needing a phone camera. Simply upload a screenshot, photo, or scanned document containing a QR code and instantly extract the embedded URL, text, WiFi password, contact information, or any other encoded data. Perfect for desktop users, developers testing QR code outputs, and anyone who receives QR codes via email or messaging apps. Free browser-based tool with no data upload — all processing happens locally on your device.', zh: '在电脑上直接从图片文件解码二维码，无需手机摄像头扫描。只需上传包含二维码的截图、照片或扫描文档，即可瞬间提取嵌入的网址链接、文字内容、WiFi密码、联系人信息或其他编码数据。非常适合桌面端用户、测试二维码输出的开发者以及通过邮件或通讯软件接收二维码的任何人。免费浏览器端工具，零数据上传——所有处理均在设备本地完成。' },
    seoContent: { en: 'QR codes are everywhere — in emails, on websites, in presentations, embedded in screenshots shared by colleagues, and printed on documents you have already scanned. But how do you decode them when you are working on your laptop or desktop computer? Our Online QR Code Scanner solves this common frustration elegantly. Simply drag and drop any image file (PNG, JPG, WebP, GIF, or BMP) containing a QR code into the tool, and it instantly extracts and displays all encoded information. Whether it is a URL link that opens in a new tab, a pre-formatted email address, a WiFi network name and password, a phone number, an SMS message, plain text, or contact card (vCard) information, the tool automatically detects the content type and presents it in the most useful format. The scanner handles QR codes of any size, at any angle, and even partially obscured codes — perfect for extracting links from social media screenshots, decoding product QR codes from online shopping images, verifying QR code outputs during development and testing, recovering information from scanned documents and PDFs, or reading QR codes shared in team chat platforms without needing to pull out your phone. Built on the battle-tested jsQR library with high fault tolerance, the tool reliably reads Micro QR codes, standard QR codes, and QR codes with embedded images or design elements. No camera access required, no data sent to any server, and instant results — making it the fastest and most privacy-respecting QR code decoding solution available online today.', zh: '二维码无处不在——在邮件里、网页上、演示文稿中、同事分享的截屏里，以及你已经扫描过的文档上。但当你在笔记本电脑或台式机上工作时，如何解码它们？我们的在线二维码识别器优雅地解决了这一常见痛点。只需将包含二维码的任意图片文件（PNG、JPG、WebP、GIF或BMP）拖拽到工具中，即刻提取并显示所有编码信息。无论是可在新标签页打开的网址链接、预填格式的邮箱地址、WiFi网络名称和密码、电话号码、短信内容、纯文本还是联系人名片（vCard）信息，工具自动检测内容类型并以最实用的格式呈现。识别器可处理任意尺寸、任意角度甚至部分遮挡的二维码——非常适合从社交媒体截图中提取链接、从网购图片中解码产品二维码、在开发和测试过程中验证二维码输出、从扫描文档和PDF中恢复信息，或在团队聊天平台中收到二维码时无需掏出手机即可读取。基于经过充分验证的jsQR库构建，具有高容错性，可可靠读取Micro QR码、标准QR码以及包含嵌入图像或设计元素的QR码。无需摄像头权限，无数据上传至任何服务器，即刻返回结果——使其成为当前线上最快、最尊重隐私的二维码解码方案。' }
