    category: 'Image',
    icon: Grid3X3,
    tags: ['社交媒体', '切图', '朋友圈', 'image', 'split'],
    seoTitle: { en: 'Image Splitter - Split Photos into Grid for Instagram WeChat Free', zh: '图片切割工具 - 免费在线九宫格切图 朋友圈小红书神器' },
    seoDescription: { en: 'Split any photo into perfectly aligned grid pieces for social media. Create stunning 3x3 Instagram grids, 2x2 WeChat Moments layouts, and 4x4 creative collages in seconds. Download all image slices as a convenient ZIP file with one click. Perfect for social media influencers, content creators, and anyone wanting to make their photo posts stand out with professional grid layouts. Free browser-based tool with no upload required — all processing happens locally on your device.', zh: '将任意照片分割为完美对齐的网格块，用于社交媒体展示。数秒内创建惊艳的Instagram九宫格、微信朋友圈四宫格和创意十六宫格拼图。一键打包下载所有切片为便捷的ZIP文件。非常适合社交媒体达人、内容创作者和任何想让照片帖子以专业网格布局脱颖而出的人。免费浏览器端工具，无需上传——所有处理在设备本地完成。' },
    seoContent: { en: 'Grid-split photos have become one of the most eye-catching formats on social media platforms like Instagram, WeChat Moments, Xiaohongshu (Little Red Book), and Weibo. A single panoramic or portrait photo split into a 3x3 grid creates a visually stunning mosaic effect that draws viewers in and encourages them to visit your profile to see the full composition. Our Image Splitter makes this process effortless — upload any photo, choose your grid layout (2x2 for clean symmetry, 3x3 for the classic Instagram puzzle, 4x4 for detailed creative compositions, or define a completely custom row and column count), and instantly download all individually numbered image slices as a neatly organized ZIP file. Each slice is pixel-perfect with mathematically precise cropping, ensuring seamless alignment when posted back-to-back on any social platform. The tool maintains your original image resolution and quality throughout the splitting process. Popular creative uses include revealing a larger artwork piece by piece (building suspense and engagement), creating collaborative photo walls where each friend posts one tile, turning travel photos into immersive grid journals, splitting event posters for multi-post promotional campaigns, and transforming product photography into engaging carousel posts that tell a visual story slide by slide. All image processing is performed entirely in your browser using Canvas API — no files are ever uploaded to any server, keeping your private photos completely confidential and secure.', zh: '网格分割照片已成为Instagram、微信朋友圈、小红书和微博等社交媒体平台上最引人注目的展示形式之一。一张全景或竖版照片分割为3x3九宫格，创造出视觉上令人惊艳的马赛克效果，吸引观看者点进你的主页查看完整构图。我们的图片切割工具让这一过程毫不费力——上传任意照片，选择网格布局（2x2简约对称、3x3经典Instagram拼图、4x4精细创意构图，或自定义行列数量），即刻将所有带编号的图片切片以整齐的ZIP文件下载。每张切片都是像素级精确的数学裁切，确保在任何社交平台上连续发布时完美无缝对齐。工具在整个分割过程中保持原始图片的分辨率和画质。流行的创意用法包括逐张揭示一幅大型艺术作品（营造悬念和互动）、创建协作照片墙让每位朋友各发一块、将旅行照片转化为沉浸式网格日记、为多帖推广活动分割活动海报，以及将产品摄影转化为逐张讲述视觉故事的轮播帖。所有图片处理完全在浏览器中使用Canvas API完成——文件永远不会上传至任何服务器，确保您的私人照片完全保密和安全。' }
