    tags: ['text', 'clean'],
    seoTitle: { en: 'Text Deduplicator - Remove Duplicate Lines & Sort Online Free', zh: '文本去重工具 - 在线删除重复行并排序 免费' },
    seoDescription: { en: 'Instantly remove duplicate lines from any text list, sort entries alphabetically (A-Z or Z-A) or numerically (ascending or descending), and clean up messy data with automatic whitespace trimming. Perfect for cleaning email lists, deduplicating keyword research data, organizing log file analysis results, merging multiple lists without duplicates, and preparing clean data for spreadsheets and databases. Free browser-based text processing tool with one-click copy, no sign-up required.', zh: '即时删除任意文本列表中的重复行，按字母（A-Z或Z-A）或数字（升序或降序）排序条目，自动清除多余空白字符整理混乱数据。非常适合清理邮箱列表、关键词数据去重、日志文件分析结果整理、合并多个列表时剔除重复项，以及为电子表格和数据库准备干净数据。免费浏览器端文本处理工具，一键复制结果，无需注册。' },
    seoContent: { en: 'Data cleaning is one of the most tedious yet essential tasks in any professional workflow — whether you are a marketer managing email lists, a developer analyzing server logs, a content strategist consolidating keywords, or a researcher merging survey responses from multiple sources. Duplicate entries silently inflate your counts, skew your analysis, and waste your time. Our Text Deduplicator provides a blazingly fast way to clean, deduplicate, and organize any text-based list directly in your browser, without uploading anything to a server. Simply paste your list (one item per line), and with a single click, all duplicate lines are removed instantly. The tool also offers sorting modes — alphabetical A-Z for alphabetical lists (like names or tags), reverse Z-A for inverted ordering, numeric ascending for numbered entries (like IDs or quantities), and numeric descending for ranking lists. Additional cleanup options include trimming leading and trailing whitespace from each line, removing completely empty lines, and stripping HTML tags if your data was copied from a web page. The line count indicator shows you exactly how many entries you started with versus how many remain after cleanup, so you can instantly see how many duplicates were removed. Common real-world use cases include cleaning email subscriber lists before importing into a new CRM, deduplicating keyword research exports from tools like Ahrefs or SEMrush, merging contact lists from multiple team members without duplicates, organizing user feedback and survey responses, cleaning server log analysis results, preparing clean data imports for Excel, Google Sheets, or SQL databases, and removing duplicate URLs when building a sitemap. All text processing is performed entirely in your browser memory — no data is ever sent to any server, uploaded to the cloud, or stored anywhere, ensuring complete privacy for your potentially sensitive business data.', zh: '数据清理是任何专业工作流程中最繁琐但最必不可少的任务之一——无论您是管理邮箱列表的营销人员、分析服务器日志的开发者、整合关键词的内容策略师，还是合并多个来源的调研回答的研究人员。重复条目会悄悄夸大计数、扭曲分析结果并浪费您的时间。我们的文本去重工具提供了一种极速的方式来在浏览器中直接清理、去重和整理任何基于文本的列表，无需上传任何内容到服务器。只需粘贴您的列表（每行一个条目），单击一次，所有重复行即刻清除。工具还提供排序模式——字母升序A-Z用于字母类列表（如姓名或标签）、字母降序Z-A用于倒序排列、数字升序用于编号条目（如ID或数量）、数字降序用于排行榜类列表。额外的清理选项包括去除每行的首尾空白字符、删除完全空白行，以及如果数据是从网页复制则去除HTML标签。行数指示器精确显示清理前后各有多少条目，让您一眼看到删除了多少重复项。常见的实际使用场景包括在导入新CRM之前清理邮箱订阅列表、对来自Ahrefs或SEMrush等工具的关键词研究导出数据进行去重、合并多个团队成员的联系人列表而不产生重复、整理用户反馈和调研回复、清理服务器日志分析结果、为Excel、Google Sheets或SQL数据库准备干净的导入数据，以及在构建网站站点地图时去除重复URL。所有文本处理完全在浏览器内存中完成——数据永远不会发送至任何服务器、上传到云端或存储在任何地方，确保您潜在的敏感业务数据完全隐私。' }
