    seoTitle: { en: 'Hash Generator - MD5 SHA1 SHA256 Online Free Tool', zh: '在线哈希生成器 - MD5 SHA1 SHA256加密工具免费' },
    seoDescription: { en: 'Generate MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256, SHA-384, and SHA-512 cryptographic hashes instantly for any text or file input. Compare hash outputs side by side across algorithms, verify file integrity with checksums, and generate secure password hashes. An essential free online tool for software developers verifying download integrity, security engineers analyzing hash collisions, blockchain developers working with transaction hashes, and system administrators generating password storage hashes. All processing happens locally in your browser with streaming support for large files.', zh: '为任意文本或文件输入即时生成MD5、SHA-1、SHA-256、SHA-384和SHA-512加密哈希值。并排对比各算法的哈希输出，用校验和验证文件完整性，生成安全的密码哈希。对于验证下载完整性的软件开发者、分析哈希碰撞的安全工程师、处理交易哈希的区块链开发者以及生成密码存储哈希的系统管理员来说，这是必备的免费在线工具。所有处理在浏览器本地完成，支持大文件流式处理。' },
    seoContent: { en: 'Cryptographic hash functions are the unsung heroes of modern computing — they silently protect password databases, verify that software downloads have not been tampered with, power blockchain consensus mechanisms, detect duplicate files in storage systems, and enable digital signatures and certificate authorities. Understanding and using hash functions correctly is a fundamental skill for any developer working with security, data integrity, or distributed systems. Our Hash Generator provides instant access to the five most widely used hash algorithms in a single, clean interface. Choose from MD5 (128-bit, fast but cryptographically broken — useful only for non-security purposes like checksums and data deduplication), SHA-1 (160-bit, being phased out due to collision vulnerabilities but still found in legacy Git commit hashes and some SSL certificates), SHA-256 (256-bit, the current gold standard — used in Bitcoin mining, SSL/TLS certificates, JWT token signatures, and password hashing), SHA-384, and SHA-512 (the strongest options, used in high-security government and military applications). Type or paste any text to see all hash outputs computed simultaneously in real-time, making side-by-side comparison effortless. The file mode supports hashing large files up to several hundred megabytes using streaming technologies that process the file in chunks without loading it entirely into memory — perfect for verifying downloaded ISO images, software installers, database backups, and large media files against published checksums. Each hash is displayed with a convenient copy-to-clipboard button. Common professional use cases include generating MD5 or SHA-256 checksums to verify download integrity of Linux distributions, software packages, and firmware updates, computing file hashes to detect duplicate files in storage systems, generating content-addressable identifiers for distributed file systems (IPFS, Git), hashing user passwords before storage (with SHA-256 as part of a proper salted hashing scheme), creating cache-busting file names for web assets, detecting unauthorized modifications to configuration files via hash comparison, generating unique identifiers from data content in database systems, and verifying blockchain transaction and block hashes. Important security note: While this tool makes it easy to generate hashes, proper secure password storage requires dedicated key derivation functions like bcrypt, scrypt, argon2, or PBKDF2 with thousands of iterations and random salts — never store passwords with a single round of SHA-256. All hashing operations are computed entirely in your browser using the Web Crypto API — no data ever leaves your computer, making this tool safe for hashing proprietary source code, confidential documents, and password material.', zh: '加密哈希函数是现代计算的无声英雄——它们默默保护着密码数据库、验证软件下载未被篡改、驱动区块链共识机制、检测存储系统中的重复文件，以及支持数字签名和证书颁发机构。正确理解和使用哈希函数是任何从事安全、数据完整性或分布式系统开发的开发者的基本技能。我们的哈希生成器在单一简洁界面中提供对五种最广泛使用的哈希算法的即时访问。从以下算法中选择：MD5（128位，速度快但已被密码学攻破——仅适用于校验和、数据去重等非安全用途）、SHA-1（160位，因碰撞漏洞正在逐步淘汰，但仍存在于旧版Git提交哈希和某些SSL证书中）、SHA-256（256位，当前的金标准——用于比特币挖矿、SSL/TLS证书、JWT令牌签名和密码哈希）、SHA-384和SHA-512（最强大的选项，用于高安全性的政府和军事应用）。输入或粘贴任意文本，即可实时查看同时计算出的所有哈希输出，让并排对比毫不费力。文件模式支持对高达数百兆字节的大文件进行哈希处理，使用流式技术分块处理文件而不将其全部加载到内存中——非常适合根据已发布的校验和验证下载的ISO镜像、软件安装包、数据库备份和大型媒体文件。每个哈希值都配有便捷的一键复制到剪贴板按钮。常见专业用例包括生成MD5或SHA-256校验和以验证Linux发行版、软件包和固件更新的下载完整性，计算文件哈希以检测存储系统中的重复文件，为分布式文件系统（IPFS、Git）生成内容寻址标识符，在存储前对用户密码进行哈希处理（使用SHA-256作为适当加盐哈希方案的一部分），为网页资源创建缓存破坏文件名，通过哈希比对检测配置文件是否被未授权修改，在数据库系统中从数据内容生成唯一标识符，以及验证区块链交易和区块哈希。重要安全提醒：虽然此工具使生成哈希变得简单，但正确的安全密码存储需要专用的密钥派生函数，如bcrypt、scrypt、argon2或PBKDF2，配合数千次迭代和随机盐——永远不要用单次SHA-256来存储密码。所有哈希操作使用Web Crypto API完全在浏览器中计算——任何数据都不会离开您的电脑，使该工具对于哈希处理专有源代码、机密文档和密码材料完全安全。' }
