    description: { en: 'Play Chinese Chess (Xiangqi) with full authentic rules against an AI opponent or a friend. Features include river and palace zone enforcement, cannon (炮) special movement, flying general rule, and perpetual check detection. The most culturally significant board game in Chinese history, now playable online for free.', zh: '与AI对手或好友对弈中国象棋（象棋），完全遵循中国传统规则。功能包括河界和九宫格区域限制、炮的特殊翻山吃子规则、飞将规则和长将检测。中国历史上最具文化意义的棋盘游戏，现在可免费在线体验。' },
    category: 'Entertainment',
    icon: Dices,
    tags: ['game', 'ai', 'board', 'xiangqi'],
    seoTitle: { en: 'Play Chinese Chess Xiangqi Online Free with AI Opponent', zh: '免费在线中国象棋 - 人机对战AI中国象棋' },
    seoDescription: { en: 'Play traditional Chinese Chess (Xiangqi or 中国象棋) online for free against an intelligent AI opponent or with friends in local two-player mode. Features full authentic rule implementation including river and palace zone movement restrictions, cannon (炮) special capture mechanics, flying general rule enforcement, and perpetual check detection. Beautiful traditional Chinese-style board design with Chinese character pieces and smooth animations. Available in both Chinese and English interfaces. Perfect for Chinese culture enthusiasts, strategy game lovers, students learning traditional board games, and anyone interested in experiencing one of the world is oldest and most strategic board games.', zh: '免费在线体验传统中国象棋（象棋），可与智能AI对手对弈或与朋友本地双人对战。完全实现传统中国象棋规则，包括楚河汉界和九宫格区域移动限制、炮的特殊翻山吃子机制、飞将（将帅对面）规则执行以及长将长捉违规检测。精美中国传统风格棋盘设计，汉字棋子配合流畅动画。支持中英文双语界面显示。非常适合中国文化爱好者、策略游戏爱好者、学习传统棋盘游戏的学生，以及任何对体验世界上最古老、最具策略性的棋盘游戏之一感兴趣的人。' },
    seoContent: { en: 'Chinese Chess (Xiangqi, 中国象棋 or 象棋) is one of the most popular and culturally significant board games in the world, with a history spanning over a thousand years and an estimated hundreds of millions of active players primarily across China and East and Southeast Asia. While sharing a common ancestry with international chess (both descended from the ancient Indian game Chaturanga), Xiangqi has evolved its own unique and fascinating set of rules that reflect traditional Chinese military strategy and philosophy: a board divided by a river (楚河汉界 — the Chu River and Han Border, referencing the Chu-Han Contention period in Chinese history), a palace zone (九宫) that restricts the movement of the general and advisors, distinctive pieces including the cannon (炮) that captures by jumping over exactly one intervening piece, elephants (象) that cannot cross the river and move in a diagonal 田-shape pattern, and the unique flying general rule that forbids the two generals from facing each other directly on an open file. Our online Xiangqi game faithfully implements all these authentic rules, making it an excellent way to experience this profound strategic tradition whether you are a native player or a newcomer curious about Chinese culture. The AI opponent analyzes positions using heuristic evaluation considering material value, piece activity, king safety, and positional factors specific to Xiangqi, providing engaging gameplay across multiple difficulty settings. The local two-player mode allows face-to-face matches on the same device. The board features elegant Chinese aesthetics with traditional character marks for each intersection point, smooth piece-lifting and placement animations, and clear visual indicators for the river, palace zones, and piece ownership. Whether you are a lifelong Xiangqi enthusiast practicing strategy against an always-available opponent, a Chinese culture lover exploring traditional pastimes, a parent passing down cultural heritage to the next generation, or an international chess player curious about how this parallel evolution of chess developed its own beautiful strategic identity, this free online Chinese Chess platform provides an authentic, respectful, and thoroughly enjoyable playing experience with zero barriers to entry.', zh: '中国象棋（象棋）是世界上最受欢迎、最具文化意义的棋盘游戏之一，拥有超过千年的悠久历史，在中国及东亚、东南亚地区拥有数亿活跃玩家。虽然与国际象棋有共同渊源（均源自古代印度的恰图兰卡游戏），但中国象棋演化出了一套独特而引人入胜的规则，反映了中国传统军事战略和哲学思想：以楚河汉界分隔的棋盘（指代中国历史上楚汉相争时期）、限制将帅和士活动范围的九宫区域、必须翻山（跳过一个棋子）才能吃子的炮、不能过河且走田字形对角线的象，以及禁止两将直接对面（飞将）的独特规则。我们的在线中国象棋忠实实现所有这些传统规则，无论您是本土玩家还是对中国文化充满好奇的新手，都是体验这一深厚战略传统的绝佳方式。AI对手使用启发式评估分析局面，综合考虑子力价值、棋子活跃度、将帅安全性和中国象棋特定的局面因素，在多个难度设置下提供引人入胜的对弈体验。本地双人模式支持在同一设备上进行面对面对弈。棋盘采用优雅的中式美学设计，带有每个交叉点的传统标记、流畅的提子和落子动画，以及河界、九宫格区域和棋子归属的清晰视觉指示。无论您是希望与随时可用的对手练习策略的终身象棋爱好者、探索传统娱乐方式的中国文化爱好者、将文化遗产传递给下一代的家长，还是对这项与国际象棋平行演化并发展出自身优美战略个性的游戏感到好奇的国际象棋玩家，这款免费在线中国象棋平台都能提供真实、尊重且彻底愉悦的游戏体验，零入门门槛。' }
