    tags: ['dev', 'css', 'design'],
    seoTitle: { en: 'CSS Glassmorphism Generator - Create Frosted Glass UI Effects Free', zh: 'CSS毛玻璃特效生成器 - 免费在线创建玻璃拟态UI效果' },
    seoDescription: { en: 'Create stunning CSS glassmorphism (frosted glass) UI effects with a real-time visual editor. Customize backdrop blur intensity, background color and opacity, border width and color, box shadow depth, corner border radius, and overall card dimensions. See every change instantly in the live preview and copy the production-ready CSS code with one click. Perfect for web designers creating modern Apple/iOS-style interfaces, frontend developers implementing trendy frosted glass card components, and UI/UX designers prototyping glassmorphism dashboard panels, login forms, and modal dialogs.', zh: '使用实时可视化编辑器创建令人惊艳的CSS玻璃拟态（毛玻璃）UI特效。自定义背景模糊强度、背景颜色和不透明度、边框宽度和颜色、阴影深度、圆角半径和卡片整体尺寸。在实时预览中即时查看每一次更改，并一键复制可用于生产环境的CSS代码。非常适合创建现代Apple/iOS风格界面的网页设计师、实现潮流磨砂玻璃卡片组件的前端开发者，以及原型化玻璃拟态仪表板面板、登录表单和模态对话框的UI/UX设计师。' },
    seoContent: { en: 'Glassmorphism (also called glass morphism or frosted glass UI) has become one of the most popular and visually striking UI design trends in recent years, popularized by Apple is macOS Big Sur, iOS control center, Windows 11 is Fluent Design, and countless modern web applications. The effect mimics the look of frosted glass — a semi-transparent panel that blurs the content behind it while casting subtle shadows and reflections, creating a beautiful sense of depth and layering without the heaviness of traditional opaque cards. Our CSS Glassmorphism Generator lets you design this effect visually and interactively, without writing a single line of CSS manually. Configure the core glassmorphism properties through intuitive sliders: backdrop blur (controls how much the background content is blurred through the glass), background color with alpha transparency (white with 10-30% opacity is classic, but colored tints create stunning variations), border color and width (subtle white borders enhance the glass illusion), box shadow (creates depth and separation from the background), and border radius (rounded corners complete the modern aesthetic). A live preview area shows the effect applied to a realistic card component with sample text content, so you see exactly how it will look in a real web application. Adjust your background image or gradient behind the preview to test how the glass effect behaves over different backgrounds — light backgrounds, dark backgrounds, complex images, or colorful gradients. Once you are satisfied with the appearance, copy the generated CSS with one click and paste it directly into your project stylesheets. The output is clean, minimal CSS using backdrop-filter with appropriate fallbacks for older browsers. Whether you are designing a modern SaaS dashboard with glass panels, creating an iOS-style weather app UI, building a trendy portfolio website with frosted navigation bars, or implementing glassmorphism cards for a landing page, this free generator saves you hours of trial-and-error in your CSS inspector while delivering professional, polished results. All design work is done in your browser — no data collection, no account required, and instant results.', zh: '玻璃拟态（Glassmorphism，也称毛玻璃UI或玻璃质感设计）已成为近年来最流行、视觉效果最引人注目的UI设计趋势之一，由Apple的macOS Big Sur、iOS控制中心、Windows 11的Fluent Design以及无数现代Web应用推广开来。这种效果模仿了磨砂玻璃的外观——一个半透明的面板，模糊其背后的内容，同时投射微妙的阴影和反射，创造出美丽的深度感和层次感，而没有传统不透明卡片的沉重感。我们的CSS毛玻璃特效生成器让您以可视化和交互方式设计这种效果，无需手动编写一行CSS代码。通过直观的滑块配置玻璃拟态核心属性：背景模糊（控制背景内容透过玻璃的模糊程度）、带alpha透明度的背景色（白色配合10-30%不透明度是经典选择，但彩色色调可创造惊艳变化）、边框颜色和宽度（微妙的白色边框增强玻璃质感）、盒阴影（创造深度感和与背景的分离感）和边框圆角（圆角完成现代美学）。实时预览区域将效果应用于包含示例文本内容的逼真卡片组件，让您精确看到它在真实Web应用中的外观。在预览后方调整背景图片或渐变，测试玻璃效果在不同背景上的表现——浅色背景、深色背景、复杂图片或多彩渐变。一旦满意外观效果，一键复制生成的CSS并直接粘贴到项目样式表中。输出的CSS简洁、最小化，使用backdrop-filter并配有为旧版浏览器的适当降级方案。无论您是在设计带有玻璃面板的现代SaaS仪表板、创建iOS风格的天气App界面、构建带有磨砂导航栏的潮流作品集网站，还是为落地页实现玻璃拟态卡片，这款免费生成器都能为您节省数小时在CSS检查器中的试错时间，同时输出专业、精致的成果。所有设计工作在浏览器中完成——无数据收集、无需账户、即时获得结果。' }
